Package com.flipkart.dao

Interface FlipFitGymOwnerDAOInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
FlipFitGymOwnerDAO
public interface FlipFitGymOwnerDAOInterface
Interface for FlipFit Gym Owner DAO (Data Access Object). This interface defines methods for gym owner-related operations such as registering gym owners, managing gyms, adding/removing gym slots, and viewing gym details.
